{
  "chapter": 62,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十二回 全面行动\n\n小方在深夜遭遇三名杀手围攻。第一名杀手胡大麟文雅规矩却身经百战，被小方一剑封喉。灰衣人林正雄（马沙）假意与小方交谈，实为第三名杀手，趁小方分心时从袖中抽出软剑偷袭，却被小方反杀。沙平现身，自称是吕三派来观战的使者，带走三具尸体。小方让沙平转告吕三保重自己，暗示将亲自去找吕三算账。班察巴那已布下天罗地网追踪沙平行踪，但沙平成功摆脱追踪，将尸体运至柳州张记棺材铺。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "text": "你也是来杀我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡大麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "text": "你认得我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡大麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "text": "我们有仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡大麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "text": "你为什么要杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡大麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我要杀你，只因为你是小方，要命的小方。你可以要别人的命，别人为什么不能要你的命？这理由够不够？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_lin",
      "text": "够了。绝对够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们当然也是来杀我的。你们不妨同时出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我不好。我好好的睡觉，却有人无缘无故的要来杀我，我怎么会好？",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果我好好的躺在床上，忽然有三个人要来杀我，我也会觉得很倒楣的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "只有三个人要来杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只有三个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "你呢？你不是来杀我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你应该看得出我不是。我们无冤无仇，我为什么要杀你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "他们也和我无冤无仇，他们为什么要来杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他们是奉命而来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "奉谁的命？吕三？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，现在他们三个人里已经有两个死在你的剑下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "第三个呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "第三个人当然是最可怕的一个。比前面两个人加起来都可怕。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "第一个去杀你的人叫胡大麟，第二个叫杜永。他们的剑法都不弱，杀人的经验也很丰富。我实在想不到，你能在一招内就取他们的性命。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你的剑法实在比他们估计中高得多。",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "那也许只因为他们的剑法比他们自己的估计差多了。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是第三个人就不同了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "第三个人才是真正懂得杀人的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "前面两个人死在你的剑下，就因为他们不能知己知彼。他们不但高估了自己，而且低估了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是第三个人对你的出身家世和武功经验都已了若指掌。因为他没有到这里来杀你之前，已经把你这个人彻底研究过，而且刚才还把你杀人出手的动作看得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你呢？你对他这个人知道多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我一点都不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以你在这一方面已经落了下风！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你站着的地方，是个很空旷的地方，从四面八方都可以看得到你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道他在哪里？看不看得见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我看不见，只不过我也许可以猜想得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "他一定已经到了我的身后，就在我刚才全神贯注在你身上的时候，他就从另一边绕到我后面去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你猜得不错。",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "现在他说不定就站在我后面，说不定已经距离我很近，说不定一伸手就可以杀了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以你一直不敢回头看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "不错，我的确不敢回头。因为如果回头去看，身法上一定会有破绽露出来，他就有机会杀我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你不想给他这种机会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我当然不想。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你就算不回头，他也一样有机会可以杀你的。从背后出手杀人总比当面刺杀要容易些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "虽然容易一点，也不能算太容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "因为我还没有死，还不是死人。我还有耳朵可以听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是不是听出他出手时的风声？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果他的出手很慢，根本没有风声呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "不管他的出手多慢，我总会有感觉的。我练剑十余年，走江湖也走了十余年，如果我连这一点感觉都没有，我怎么会活到现在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有理。绝对有理。",
      "tone": "赞同",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "所以他如果要出手杀我，就一定要考虑后果。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "后果？什么后果？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "他要我的命，我也会要他的命。就算他能把我刺杀在他的剑下，我也绝不会让他活着回去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你真的有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我当然有！不但我自己相信自己有这种把握，连他都一定相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "如果他不认为我有这种把握，为什么直等到现在还不出手？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "也许他还在等。等到有更好的机会才出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "他等不到的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那么你就不该跟我说话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "无论什么人在说话的时候，注意力都难免会分散。那时候他就有机会了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "你知不知道刚才附近发生了什么事？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我知道。就在你走到这棵树下的时候，树上有一只松鼠钻进了洞穴，震动了六片叶子。我们开始说话的时候，左面荒地里有一条蝮蛇吞下了一只田鸡。一条黄鼠狼刚从前面的山脚下跑过去。后面客栈里有一对夫妇醒了。客栈老板养的一只馋猫正在厨房里偷鱼吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你说的是真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "绝对不假。不管我在干什么，附近一二十丈内的动静，都逃不过我的耳目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "还好我不是来杀你的。否则现在我说不定也已经死在你的剑下。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你既然明知他要杀你，既然明知他在你的身后，为什么不先出手杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "因为我不急，急的是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "是他要来杀我，不是我要杀他。我当然比他沉得住气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我佩服你，真的佩服你。如果我们不是在这种情况下相见，我真希望交你这么样一个朋友。",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "现在我们为什么不能交朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我是跟他们一起来的，你多少总不免对我有些提防之心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "你错了！如果我看不出你的用心，怎么会跟你说话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我还是可以交你这个朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "为什么不可以？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是你根本不知道我是个什么样的人。你甚至连我的姓名都不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "你可以告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "当然可以。",
      "tone": "愉快",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "林正雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我姓林，叫林正雄，我的朋友都叫我马沙。",
      "tone": "愉快",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "马沙！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "方伟",
      "listener": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "text": "我姓方，叫方伟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "林正雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道！我早就听见过你的名字。",
      "tone": "愉快",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "林正雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "小心，小心后面。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "精彩。精彩绝伦。",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我本来以为你一定活不成了。想不到死的居然是他。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "我自己也想不到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你什么时候才想到他才是真正第三个要杀你的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "他走过来的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那时候连我都认为你已经愿意交他这个朋友了，你怎么会想到他要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "因为他走路走得太小心了，就好像深怕会踩死蚂蚁一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "小心一点有什么不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "只有一点。像我们这样的江湖人，就算踩死七八百只蚂蚁也不在乎的。他走路走得那么小心，只不过因为他还在提防着我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "赞同",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "只有自己心里想去害人的人，才会去提防别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "我有过这种经验。吃亏上当的，通常都是不想去害人的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "就因为他们没有害人之意，所以才没有防人之心。如果你也曾有过这种经验，你就会明白我的意思了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我明白你的意思，可是我没有这种经验。因为我从来都没有相信过任何人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "也许就因为你曾经有过这种经验，已经受到过惨痛的教训，所以现在你还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "也许是的。愚我一次，其错在你；愚我两次，其错在我。如果我受到过一次教训后，还不知警惕，我就真的该死了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "说得好。",
      "tone": "赞同",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "你呢？你是不是来杀我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "你是不是吕三的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "是不是跟他们一起来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。我们都是奉吕三之命而来的，只不过我们得到的命令不同而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他们三人是奉命来杀你，我只不过奉命来看看而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "看什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "看你们怎样杀人，不管是他们杀了你，还是你杀了他们，我都要看得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经看得很清楚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "那么现在你是不是已经应该走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。只不过我还要求你一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我要带他们回去。不管他们是死是活，我都要带他们回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你肯不肯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "他们活着时对我连一点用处都没有，死了还有什么用？我为什么要留下他们？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "只不过我也希望你能替我做一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 566,
